    "text": "The old commodity-trade adage says that the Middle East “sells hydrocarbons to buy carbohydrates.”\n\nIt’s important to remember the Persian Gulf region isn’t a breadbasket as Russia and Ukraine are (now and in 2022). So the impact of the war isn’t the same in food commodities.",
